可唔可以咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講多啲依行啲資料比我 <br />\n例如做啲咩個啲"},{"pid":"963f52123dd346ad6b7f9017b61d6edbf3105fbf","tid":229453,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>design囉 工程係更加深入某一範疇<br />\n<br />\n不過你design唔識工程多數都係行唔通</blockquote><br />\n邊科design? <br />\n我識其中一科工程 但唔係建築個啲好似幫助唔大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df23b54e7d039f0e1613a6ea46dc46d925f4be9","tid":229453,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BIM 大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大概知係咩但有咩關係 巴打可唔可以講詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝"},{"pid":"64ffc547502e0fed3f38cdc6ec966ff8e91a8a73","tid":229453,"uid":54904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BIM 大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大概知係咩但有咩關係 巴打可唔可以講詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝</blockquote><br />\nBuilding information modelling <br />\n你可以download個revit黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d195a603b82cf727f9fce07cf5efe95ef7439b49","tid":229453,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"Architect"},{"pid":"028d403ce9222943ad9d87d595f6197c278ec6df","tid":229453,"uid":11059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BIM 大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大概知係咩但有咩關係 巴打可唔可以講詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝</blockquote><br />\nBuilding information modelling <br />\n你可以download個revit黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地都話知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識用BIM都係做draftman<br />\n答咩大勢所趨 九唔搭八<br />\n<br />\n回樓主 Archi係最接近design<br />\n不過現實中好多時都要睇業主要求去決定design<br />\n未必可以如你預期咁design layout<br />\n<br />\n利申：測量狗"},{"pid":"91d71c48901ac01bf009fef2b51ecab5b03790dd","tid":229453,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"香港做則師因為土地同商業考慮 DESIGN會好局限<br />\n但如果你講做DESIGN的確得architect係接近 其他果D都唔關事"},{"pid":"1427660545f69d02ed69dcd719e125f71dedd410","tid":229453,"uid":74687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"Archi啦<br />\n其實三個做嘅嘢都唔同，archi負責設計個樣，engine就拎住architect張design諗點樣同用乜材料起<br />\n所以如果係想design嘅話應該archi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197426c51ea20acdad5f6ff88571e0b54e6e8750","tid":229453,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BIM 大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大概知係咩但有咩關係 巴打可唔可以講詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝</blockquote><br />\nBuilding information modelling <br />\n你可以download個revit黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地都話知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識用BIM都係做draftman<br />\n答咩大勢所趨 九唔搭八<br />\n<br />\n回樓主 Archi係最接近design<br />\n不過現實中好多時都要睇業主要求去決定design<br />\n未必可以如你預期咁design layout<br />\n<br />\n利申：測量狗</blockquote><br />\n我聽人講building surveying係會設計building嘅envelope同layout 想問下係咪真係自己設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我做過一份工係設計啲屋 雖然會比client叫改 但過程好有趣 所以想搵返啲差唔多野工 但由於某啲原因 就唔會再係個到做 想知出邊個景係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59558bf7d23dd99a7af224be07f60f5a84