te>Archi啦<br />\n其實三個做嘅嘢都唔同，archi負責設計個樣，engine就拎住architect張design諗點樣同用乜材料起<br />\n所以如果係想design嘅話應該archi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問下有冇得一邊做一邊進修？"},{"pid":"02b40bf6927c9e111a70a542225ef85e967da459","tid":229453,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Archi啦<br />\n其實三個做嘅嘢都唔同，archi負責設計個樣，engine就拎住architect張design諗點樣同用乜材料起<br />\n所以如果係想design嘅話應該archi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問下有冇得一邊做一邊進修？</blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe32501247f5a2607b87634d4eb3ece433717e2d","tid":229453,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Archi啦<br />\n其實三個做嘅嘢都唔同，archi負責設計個樣，engine就拎住architect張design諗點樣同用乜材料起<br />\n所以如果係想design嘅話應該archi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問下有冇得一邊做一邊進修？</blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係通常就係冇學歷/係hku/cu出嚟？"},{"pid":"3014633d0a5720869aa688d6cee7a2eccb88f64c","tid":229453,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"考dse入hku/cu archi啦<br />\n<br />\n不過收26分或以上<br />\n<br />\n同要準備portfolio"},{"pid":"22a2a386891013af303cead58e2bb14af81ab156","tid":229453,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"不過你又唔講你幾大同目標係點<br />\n<br />\n好難比意見wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a687785637b61959eb83699352682129e980c7","tid":229453,"uid":11059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BIM 大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大概知係咩但有咩關係 巴打可唔可以講詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝</blockquote><br />\nBuilding information modelling <br />\n你可以download個revit黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地都話知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識用BIM都係做draftman<br />\n答咩大勢所趨 九唔搭八<br />\n<br />\n回樓主 Archi係最接近design<br />\n不過現實中好多時都要睇業主要求去決定design<br />\n未必可以如你預期咁design layout<br />\n<br />\n利申：測量狗</blockquote><br />\n我聽人講building surveying係會設計building嘅envelope同layout 想問下係咪真係自己設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我做過一份工係設計啲屋 雖然會比client叫改 但過程好有趣 所以想搵返啲差唔多野工 但由於某啲原因 就唔會再係個到做 想知出邊個<span style=\"color: red;\">市況</span>係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\nBS呢 我真係唔太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錯既話請補充<br />\n大致上做consultant就做inspection, remedial works, maintenance等；做bd果d政府dept就做批則, check UBW等。另外, BS係可以考AP既, 但我諗都未必可以做到你想做既野。<br />\n<br />\n其實你要設計building shape同layout, 實際情況上要考慮好多野, 上面有巴打提到土地(eg gfa limits from land lease, building control etc.)同經濟(eg 點起法最好賣/租出去etc)考慮, 但建築業黎講, design 成份最高都係archi架喇。<br />\n<br />\n前景我答你唔到, 照目前情況睇, 樓市一日未爆都仲有得撈下既。"},{"pid":"c6a4fbbd60ce0f3317435e63706266fcab8812ac","tid":229453,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過你又唔講你幾大同目標係點<br />\n<br />\n好難比意見wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20開頭 <br />\n最終目標係想開間公司幫人畫圖起樓<br />\n但除左識畫圖就咩都唔識 又冇學歷<br />\n識人開公司 公司係幫人畫圖起樓<br />\n但覺得佢間公司太太太細 好似冇咩前景<br />\n想一邊跟佢學野 一邊出去社會睇下依個世界"}]}